{
  "stem": "4284.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was a housewife.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we subsisted on the very, very meager pay that my father was sent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was paid, but forced labor is just not a very [LAUGHS] well-paid occupation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The other thing that became very noticeable was that we were not allowed to have any basic outside communication.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were not allowed to own radios.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were not allowed to have subscription to newspapers or magazines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You basically sat around the house waiting for who knows what to happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In 1938, you also noticed a very substantial upheaval in the population in general.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was long before the November event, which I'll come to in a moment, because what Germany was doing at that time, including the evidence that my father had to work at the Siegfried Line, was the preparation for World War II.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This kind of came right down to the population level that many things were happening more dramatically, more rapidly, and you might say, even more significantly.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The most important thing, of course, that everybody in Germany wore uniforms, uniforms, uniforms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Everybody--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, because first of all, you were not readily going out on the street because you didn't wear a Hitler Youth uniform.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you were, of course, later on asked and forced to wear the-- the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But even when you didn't wear a uniform as a child, you were suspected of being non-Aryan, obviously Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And children would set upon you, and with their little knives that they had, threaten you, kick you, beat you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you were basically defenseless because if you involved yourself in the brawl, adults would come very quickly and beatings and abuses would get even worse.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this, of course, became increasingly restricted.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
